  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Tumor diameter &lt; 5 cm

          -  Intermediate or high grade ductal carcinoma in situ

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  No informed consent

          -  Tumor size &gt; 3,5 cm

          -  Low grade ductal carcinoma in situ

          -  Invasive carcinoma

          -  No indication for a boost
      </textblock>
